      <title>Markdown进阶语法（hexo部分不支持）</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-进阶语法"><a href="#1-进阶语法" class="headerlink" title="1. 进阶语法"></a>1. 进阶语法</h1><h2 id="1-1-换行"><a href="#1-1-换行" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 换行"></a>1.1. 换行</h2><p>连续两个以上空格+回车</p><h2 id="1-2-缩进字符"><a href="#1-2-缩进字符" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 缩进字符"></a>1.2. 缩进字符</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;#160;1/4个中文缩进</span><br><span class="line">&amp;#8194;半个中文缩进，1字符</span><br><span class="line">&amp;#8195;1个中文缩进，2字符</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>未缩进<br>&amp;#160;1&#x2F;4个中文缩进<br>&amp;#8194;半个中文缩进，1字符<br>&amp;#8195;1个中文缩进，2字符</p><h2 id="1-3-特殊符号"><a href="#1-3-特殊符号" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 特殊符号"></a>1.3. 特殊符号</h2><h3 id="1-3-1"><a href="#1-3-1" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1. \"></a>1.3.1. \</h3><p>显示字符本身</p><h3 id="1-3-2-其他符号"><a href="#1-3-2-其他符号" class="headerlink" title="1.3.2. 其他符号"></a>1.3.2. 其他符号</h3><p>具体可参考<a href="https://www.axihe.com/tools/markdown/with-html/special-symbol.html">markdown特殊符号</a><br>与<a href="https://unicode-table.com/cn/">Unicode字符码查询</a></p><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>&amp;#10084;</code></td><td>&amp;#10084;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10003;</code></td><td>&amp;#10003;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10004;</code></td><td>&amp;#10004;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10005;</code></td><td>&amp;#10005;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#1;</code></td><td>&amp;#1;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#9742;</code></td><td>&amp;#9742;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#5748;</code></td><td>&amp;#5748;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#5223;</code></td><td>&amp;#5223;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#8734;</code></td><td>&amp;#8734;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10008;</code></td><td>&amp;#10008;</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="1-4-字体、字号与颜色"><a href="#1-4-字体、字号与颜色" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 字体、字号与颜色"></a>1.4. 字体、字号与颜色</h2><p>通过内嵌HTML代码实现字体特效,字体大小(size)范围<font color=#0099ff face="黑体" size=5>[1,7]</font><br>对字体颜色的修改可查询<a href="http://xh.5156edu.com/page/z1015m9220j18754.html">HTML颜色代码表</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>color=#0099ff 黑体字体<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>微软雅黑字体<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;STCAIYUN&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>华为彩云<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">1</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=1<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">2</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=2<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">3</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=3<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">4</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=4<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">5</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=5<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">6</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=6<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">7</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=7<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color=#0099ff face="黑体">color&#x3D;#0099ff 黑体字体</font><br><font face="微软雅黑">微软雅黑字体</font><br><font face="STCAIYUN">华为彩云</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=1 face="黑体">size&#x3D;1</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=2 face="黑体">size&#x3D;2</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=3 face="黑体">size&#x3D;3</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=4 face="黑体">size&#x3D;4</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=5 face="黑体">size&#x3D;5</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=6 face="黑体">size&#x3D;6</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=7 face="黑体">size&#x3D;7</font>  </p><h2 id="1-5-注脚"><a href="#1-5-注脚" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 注脚"></a>1.5. 注脚</h2><p>在需要添加注脚的文字后加上脚注名字[^注脚名字],称为加注。 然后在文本的任意位置(一般在最后)添加脚注，脚注前必须有对应的脚注名字。<br>示范如下：</p><blockquote><p>注意需要添加空格！   </p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">basic footnote[\^1]  </span><br><span class="line">here is an inline footnote[\^2]   (inline footnote)    </span><br><span class="line">and another one[\^3]    </span><br><span class="line">and another one[\^4]    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[\^1]: basic footnote content   </span><br><span class="line">[\^3]: paragraph</span><br><span class="line">footnote</span><br><span class="line">content    </span><br><span class="line">[\^4]: footnote content with some [markdown](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown) </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>basic footnote<sup id="fnref:1"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote">1</a></sup><br>here is an inline footnote<sup id="fnref:2"><a href="#fn:2" rel="footnote">2</a></sup>   (inline footnote)<br>and another one<sup id="fnref:3"><a href="#fn:3" rel="footnote">3</a></sup><br>and another one<sup id="fnref:4"><a href="#fn:4" rel="footnote">4</a></sup>    </p><h2 id="1-6-背景色"><a href="#1-6-背景色" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 背景色"></a>1.6. 背景色</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">orange</span>&gt;</span></span>背景色是：orange<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor=orange>背景色是：orange</td></tr></table><h2 id="1-7-emoji表情"><a href="#1-7-emoji表情" class="headerlink" title="1.7. emoji表情"></a>1.7. emoji表情</h2><p>emoji表情使用:EMOJICODE:的格式，详细列表可见<a href="https://www.webpagefx.com/tools/emoji-cheat-sheet/">Emoji cheat sheet</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:smile:  </span><br><span class="line">:blush:  </span><br><span class="line">:heart<span class="emphasis">_eyes:  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">:flushed:  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">:stuck_</span>out<span class="emphasis">_tongue_</span>closed<span class="emphasis">_eyes:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>:smile:<br>:blush:<br>:heart_eyes:<br>:flushed:<br>:stuck_out_tongue_closed_eyes:<div id="footnotes"><hr><div id="footnotelist"><ol style="list-style:none; padding-left: 0;"><li id="fn:1"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">1.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;">basic footnote content</span><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li><li id="fn:3"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">3.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;">paragraph<br>footnote<br>content</span><a href="#fnref:3" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li><li id="fn:4"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">4.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;">footnote content with some <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown">markdown</a></span><a href="#fnref:4" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li></ol></div></div></p>]]></content>
      
      
