    <entry>
      <title>Markdown基本语法（hexo均支持）</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-基本语法"><a href="#1-基本语法" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本语法"></a>1. 基本语法</h1><h2 id="1-1-标题"><a href="#1-1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 标题 - #"></a>1.1. 标题 - #</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># h1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## h2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### h3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### h4</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2-段落"><a href="#1-2-段落" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 段落"></a>1.2. 段落</h2><p>Markdown划分段落非常简单，就是在段落前后保留一个空行即可</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">段落一</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">段落二</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>段落一</p><p>段落二</p><h2 id="1-3-区块引用-gt"><a href="#1-3-区块引用-gt" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 区块引用 - &gt;"></a>1.3. 区块引用 - &gt;</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用段落，高亮显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;                          # 空格</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 嵌套1</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; 嵌套2</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt; 嵌套3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>引用段落，高亮显示</p><p>嵌套1</p><blockquote><p>嵌套2</p><blockquote><p>嵌套3</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="1-4-超链接-显示文字-超链接"><a href="#1-4-超链接-显示文字-超链接" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 超链接 - [显示文字](超链接)"></a>1.4. 超链接 - [显示文字](超链接)</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">超链接显示文字</span>](<span class="link">http://www.baidu.com &quot;超链接title&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="http://www.baidu.com/" title="超链接title">超链接显示文字</a></p><h2 id="1-5-图片"><a href="#1-5-图片" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 图片 - ![]()"></a>1.5. 图片 - ![]()</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">百度logo</span>](<span class="link">https://www.baidu.com/img/bd_logo1.png?where=super</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-6-列表"><a href="#1-6-列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 列表 - +,*,-"></a>1.6. 列表 - +,*,-</h2><h3 id="1-6-1-无序列表"><a href="#1-6-1-无序列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6.1. 无序列表"></a>1.6.1. 无序列表</h3><p>不同符号最高支持到三级列表</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 段1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 段2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 段3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  *</span> 段3.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    *</span> 段3.1.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      *</span> 段3.1.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>段1</li></ul><ul><li>段2</li></ul><ul><li>段3<ul><li>段3.1<ul><li>段3.1.1</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="1-6-2-有序列表"><a href="#1-6-2-有序列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6.2. 有序列表"></a>1.6.2. 有序列表</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 段1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 段2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 段3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   1.</span> 段3.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      1.</span> 段3.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>段1</li><li>段2</li><li>段3<ol><li>段3.1<ol><li>段3.1.1</li></ol></li></ol></li></ol><h2 id="1-7-分隔线-—"><a href="#1-7-分隔线-—" class="headerlink" title="1.7. 分隔线 - ***,—"></a>1.7. 分隔线 - ***,—</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="section">---</span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><hr><h2 id="1-8-字体特效"><a href="#1-8-字体特效" class="headerlink" title="1.8. 字体特效"></a>1.8. 字体特效</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*字体1*</span>         斜体</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_字体1_</span>         斜体</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**字体2**</span>       加粗</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__字体2__</span>       加粗</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*字体3*</span>**</span>     加粗斜体</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">_字体3_</span>__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">~~字体4~~       划线</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`字体5`</span>         高亮</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">斜体</th><th align="center">加粗</th><th align="center">加粗斜体</th><th align="center">划线</th><th align="center">高亮</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"><em>字体1</em></td><td align="center"><strong>字体2</strong></td><td align="center"><em><strong>字体3</strong></em></td><td align="center"><del>字体4</del></td><td align="center"><code>字体5</code></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><em>字体1</em></td><td align="center"><strong>字体2</strong></td><td align="center"><em><strong>字体3</strong></em></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="1-9-表格"><a href="#1-9-表格" class="headerlink" title="1.9. 表格"></a>1.9. 表格</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 表头 | 表头 | 表头 |</span><br><span class="line">| :---- | ----: | :----: |    #分别为左对齐、右对齐、居中对齐</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">表头</th><th align="right">表头</th><th align="center">表头</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
